Definition.WordDefinition:
genitalia \genitalia\ n. The sex organs, especially the external sex organs, called the {external genitalia}; the genitals.
Syn: genital, genitals, private parts, privates, crotch. [WordNet 1.5]
genitalia n : external sex organ [syn: {genital organ}, {genitals}, {private parts}, {privates}, {crotch}]
